snippet.title: Health Mastery Café Ep: 33: Amber Bates: Why You Don't Want COVID 19...
snippet.description:
In this short series, I speak to everyday people who've had COVID-19 and the people on the frontline fight against it.  Each story is different; each story is designed to inform you and to compel you.    WHY YOU DON'T WANT COVID-19...from people who had it and people who treat it.  

(Video version of  the Health Mastery Café Ep: 33 - full audio at iTunes available 4/15/21)

SKIP TO: 
(17:05)- Amber describes the loss taste and smell  
(18:25) - she tells me the only thing she was able to eat after losing her taste and smell
(20:27) - Amber tells us the supplements she took
(29:56): Amber's advice for the naysayers 
**(31:40): Dr. Dave - "it doesn't play by the rules"
(33:45): Amber talks about why she's grateful
(36:04): Amber asks me a question (you can be re-infected)
**(41:04): Advice for people previously infected - to test antibodies. (vaccination)
